    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCanine Circus Presents: Dogs Do Magic\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Sunday, May 10, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 2:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: A Seating $62.50 | B Seating $51.00 | C Seating $45.25 | D Seating $39.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Family Friendly, Illusion/Circus\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Sunday, May 10, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 2:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: A Seating $62.50 | B Seating $51.00 | C Seating $45.25 | D Seating $39.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Family Friendly, Illusion/Circus\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tGet ready for an unforgettable evening of mind-blowing, hilarious comedy, and jaw-dropping canine tricks in this one-show-only spectacular! Starring one of Canada’s favorite magicians, Aaron Matthews–as seen on Disney Plus, YTV, Canada’s Wonderland, and the Calgary Stampede–this award-winning show promises excitement for all ages. Mind-Reading Dogs: These talented family pets and rescue dogs will amaze you with impossible feats and dazzling acrobatics! World-Class Canines: All trained using positive reinforcement! Magic & Comedy: Aaron blends illusions with laughter for nonstop fun! Grab your tickets now and feel the magic!\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tPerformer's Website Page\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tCanine Circus Presents: Dogs Do Magic - Official Website\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
