    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Music and Lyrics by Benny Andersson &amp; Björn Ulvaeus and some songs with Stig Anderson Book by Catherine Johnson. Originally conceived by Judy Craymer. Here we go again! Dance and sing along as we celebrate our 100th production at the Imperial Theatre with Mamma Mia! This is your chance to experience one of our top-selling shows of all time. Join us for a show packed full of fun, laughter, and unforgettable music. [maxbutton id=\"3\" url=\"https://purchase.imperialtheatre.ca/FixedSeries\" text=\"SUBSCRIBE TO SJTC\" ]"
      }
    ],
