    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "presale August 1 on sale August 16 The Alan Jackson Experience is celebrating over three decades of performing a dynamic tribute to Country Music Icon Alan Jackson. Award-winning recording artist and International Singer-Songwriter Association's Entertainer of the Year, Aaron Halliday, is a finalist once more for Entertainer, Male Vocalist, Band, Songwriter, and Single of the Year. As the longest-running and most critically acclaimed tribute to Alan Jackson, THE ALAN JACKSON EXPERIENCE continues to captivate audiences."
      }
    ],
