    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tFirst City School of Dance: There’s No Place Like Home (2 show times)\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Saturday, June 13, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 1:30 PM + 4:00 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: Adult $25 | Student $15 || Adult (Both Shows) $40 | Student (Both Shows) $22.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Dance, Family Friendly\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Saturday, June 13, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 1:30 PM + 4:00 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: Adult $25 | Student $15 || Adult (Both Shows) $40 | Student (Both Shows) $22.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Dance, Family Friendly\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tThere’s No Place Like Home is a heart-warming show about friendship, courage, and belonging.\n\n \n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
